      "G6": "NO-PII — a parcel is a place, not a person; no owner linkage / no individual wealth surveillance",
      "G7": "Murakumo-only inference (ADR-2605215000) — ToS-restricted inputs never leave the mesh",
      "G8": "OPEN-SOURCE + OPEN-DATA-FIRST — no closed AVM / closed tooling; sources open or used derived-only",
      "G9": "≥3-year provenance retention via IPFS pin (replicationMin: 2)",
      "G10": "NO-ADVICE — no investment / financial / per-person valuation advice (UPL-equivalent for appraisal); transparent reference valuations only"
    }
  },
